# Unity Scene Files
# =================
# This folder contains Unity scene files for the game.
#
# Available Scenes:
# -----------------
# - MainMenu.unity - Main menu scene with Start Game and Quit buttons
# - MainGame.unity - Main gameplay scene (to be created in Unity Editor)
#
# MainMenu Scene Contents:
# ------------------------
# The MainMenu.unity scene includes:
# - Main Camera with AudioListener
# - Managers (empty parent for GameManager, AudioManager, etc.)
# - MainMenuCanvas with:
#   - CanvasScaler (Scale with Screen Size, 1920x1080 reference)
#   - GraphicRaycaster for UI input
#   - TitleText displaying "Jacameno: Adult Life"
#   - StartButton with green background and "Start Game" text
#   - QuitButton with red background and "Quit" text
# - EventSystem with StandaloneInputModule
#
# Final Setup in Unity Editor:
# ----------------------------
# 1. Open the project in Unity 2022+
# 2. Open the MainMenu scene
# 3. Add GameManager script to the "Managers" GameObject
# 4. Add AudioManager script to the "Managers" GameObject
# 5. Add MainMenuUI script to a new "MainMenuManager" GameObject
# 6. Assign startGameButton and quitButton references in MainMenuUI
# 7. Add scene to Build Settings (File > Build Settings)
#    - MainMenu as scene index 0
#    - MainGame as scene index 1
